#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1274
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <quote>log</quote> command"
msgstr "Kommandot <quote>log</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Log command displays a dialog containing the log of the given &URL;. With "
"subversion 1.2 or above it accepts a limit, &ie; how many entries it has to "
"display."
msgstr ""
"Kommandot log visar en dialogruta som innehåller loggen från den angivna "
"webbadressen. Med Subversion 1.2 eller senare accepteras en gräns, dvs. hur "
"många poster som ska visas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Inside that dialog you may select log entries and get the differences "
"between them."
msgstr ""
"Inne i den dialogrutan kan du välja loggposter och erhålla skillnaden mellan "
"dem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display the last 20 commit logs"
msgstr "Visa de 20 senaste arkiveringsloggarna"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec log -l 20 -r HEAD&#058;1 myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec log -l 20 -r HEAD&#058;1 min-fil.c"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Beware of order of revision: You want go from HEAD to START for the LAST "
"one. So you must give revision HEAD as starting point, otherwise you would "
"get the first 20 entries."
msgstr ""
"Se upp med versionsordningen: Du vill gå från HEAD till START för den sista, "
"så du måste ange versionen HEAD som startpunkt, annars skulle du få de "
"första 20 posterna."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1289
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <quote>diff</quote> command"
msgstr "Kommandot <quote>diff</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You get differences between revisions of an item or between two items inside "
"same working copy or repository. When diff'ing revisions of an item, "
"revisions may be given as <option>-r <replaceable>STARTREV</replaceable>:"
"<replaceable>ENDREV</replaceable></option>. When diffing an item inside a "
"working copy without any revisions it prints the diff against repository."
msgstr ""
"Man får skillnader mellan versioner för ett objekt eller mellan två objekt i "
"samma arbetskopia eller arkiv. När versioner av ett objekt jämförs, kan "
"versionerna anges som <option>-r <replaceable>STARTVER</replaceable>:"
"<replaceable>SLUTVER</replaceable></option>. När ett objekt i en arbetskopia "
"jämförs utan några versioner, skrivs skillnaden mot arkivet ut."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print difference against repository, &ie; local changes"
msgstr "Skriv ut skillnader mot arkivet, dvs. lokala ändringar"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec diff myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec diff min-fil.c"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1297
#, no-c-format
msgid "Print difference between revisions"
msgstr "Skriv ut skillnader mellan versioner"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdesvn exec diff -r 21:20 myfile.c"
msgstr "kdesvn exec diff -r 21:20 min-fil.c"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When diffing two items revisions may be appended to &URL; of items. &eg;:"
msgstr ""
"När två objekt jämförs kan versioner läggas till i objektens webbadresser, "
"exempelvis:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1303
#, no-c-format
msgid "http://server/path/item?rev=HEAD"
msgstr "http://server/path/item?rev=HEAD"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid "Diffing two tagged versions"
msgstr "Jämförelse av två taggade versioner"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: index.docbook:1306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"kdesvn exec diff http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_2 "
"http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_3"
msgstr ""
"kdesvn exec diff http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_2 "
"http://www.alwins-world.de/repos/kdesvn/tags/rel_0_6_3"

