#, no-c-format
msgid "&underFDL; &underGPL;"
msgstr "&underFDL; &underGPL;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:2254
#, no-c-format
msgid "Syntax for revisions"
msgstr "Syntax för versioner"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2255
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Revisions may be given in the same form as for the standard "
"<application>svn</application> client. That means: number, keyword or date."
msgstr ""
"Versioner kan anges på samma form som i den vanliga klienten "
"<application>svn</application>. Det betyder: nummer, nyckelord eller datum."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Nummer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A number greater or equal -1. -1 means <quote>unspecified revision</quote>, "
"0 is the beginning. Normally, these numbers should not be used (most "
"operations will fail with that)."
msgstr ""
"Ett nummer större än eller lika med -1. Värdet -1 betyder "
"<quote>ospecificerad version</quote>, 0 är början. Normalt ska dessa nummer "
"inte användas (de flesta åtgärder misslyckas med det)."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2269
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyword"
msgstr "Nyckelord"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid "One of"
msgstr "En av"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2274
#, no-c-format
msgid "HEAD"
msgstr "HEAD"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid "BASE"
msgstr "BASE"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2282
#, no-c-format
msgid "COMMITED"
msgstr "COMMITED"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2286
#, no-c-format
msgid "PREV"
msgstr "PREV (Föregående)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2290
#, no-c-format
msgid "START"
msgstr "START"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2294
#, no-c-format
msgid "WORKING"
msgstr "WORKING"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keywords are case sensitive! For example, head is not the same as HEAD."
msgstr ""
"Nyckelorden är skiftlägeskänsliga. Exempelvis är inte head samma sak som "
"HEAD."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:2308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2309
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Date in form {YYYY-MM-DD}. It must real MM or DD - &eg; 2005-1-1 must be "
"written as {2005-01-01}."
msgstr ""
"Datum på formen {ÅÅÅÅ-MM-DD}. De måste använda MM eller DD - t.ex. måste "
"2005-1-1 skrivas som {2005-01-01}."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2317
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Appending a specific revision to an &URL; will always made via <quote>?"
"rev=<replaceable>revision</replaceable></quote>."
msgstr ""
"Att lägga till en specifik version till en webbadress görs alltid via "
"<quote>?rev=<replaceable>version</replaceable></quote>."

